These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, colombian, brazilian, indian, australian, malaysian
1. the pakistani is in the middle##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the indian is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the japanese is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left##1
6. the australian is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | brazilian | indian | pakistani | colombian | japanese | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, architect, fisherman, journalist, chef, photographer, firefighter
1. the firefighter is on the far right##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the chef##1
4. the chef is on the left of the fisherman##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the photographer##1
6. the firefighter is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | freelancer | chef | fisherman | photographer | journalist | architect | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, traveling, writing, reading, chess, baking
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | chess | traveling | baking | collecting | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
