.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, goat, pony, cat, ferret, fish
1. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | fish | goat | pony | ferret | hamster | bird | cat |

