.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, comedy, epic, romance, scientific, time-travel, mystery
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy | musical | time-travel | romance | mystery | epic |

